posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Centerline', 'Our touring schedules and operating hours may vary as we continue to follow local phased opening guidelines and direction from local health officials.', 'Please visit our community website for up to date information.', 'Experience Seattle living at Centerline.', 'With substantial first floor retail, a private/public interior courtyard, roof-top decks with dog areas, BBQ and green roofs bring a real community feeling to the building.', "At Centerline you're right at home.", 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 216', 'OR Text', '216', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text with us.', 'Interested In This Unit?', 'Use this link for more details:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 669 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Floor-to-Ceiling Windows', '- Modern Kitchens', '- Wood-Style Flooring', '- Brand New Apartments', '- Generous Closets', 'Community Amenities', '- Parking Garage', '- Interior Courtyard', '- Rooftop Decks & BBQ Areas', '- Ground Floor Retail', '- Green Roofs', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly, contact for details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'Centerline', '1420 NE 65th', 'St, Seattle, WA, 98115', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', '9zr1L49JQ']
